  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA56">
<l>tirumaṅkai niṉṟaruḷun teyvanā vāḻttuṅ</l>
<l>karumaṅ kaṭaippaṭumiṉ kaṇṭī – rurimaiyā</l>
<l>lēttiṉōm pāta miruntaṭakkai yentaipēr</l>
<l>nāṟṟicaiyuṅ kēṭṭīrē nām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look, fullfill the task of lauding with [your] tongues the god</l>
<l>who is ever gracious towards the young woman Śrī. Suitably</l>
<l>we praised the names of our Father, with large feet [and] broad hands;</l>
<l>did you hear<note xml:lang="en" place="foot">Here -ē seems best interpreted as an interrogative particle.</note> it in all four directions?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
